Describes the physical location of a resource.

Relates to Activity E7 with P7
Relates to Heritage Resource E18 with P53
Relates to Heritage Resource Group E27 with P89
Relates to Actor E39 with P74 (this restricts the place to former and current residences, which can be as broad or narrow)
Relates to Historical Event E5 with P7
Relates to Information Resource E73 with P67
